
How to install the nginx on linux (Ubuntu 22.04)
----------------------------------------------------

#Let's use the command to be used for installing nginx

#Before installing, we will get update the apt
sudo apt-get update -y

#nginx installation command...
sudo apt-get install nginx -y

#Check the status of nginx service is or not...Let's check
sudo systemctl status nginx

#Explore the nginx directories

cd /etc/nginx

ls -las

#If you want to restart the nginx service...
sudo systemctl restart nginx

#Or you can use the folloing command to stop and start the nginx
sudo systemctl stop nginx
sudo systemctl start nginx
sudo systemctl status nginx
